---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Recverse – Make technology practical"
  description="Do you feel like technology is moving faster than your business can keep up? We show you how to use AI and digital tools in a practical way — with less friction, clearer processes, and measurable efficiency gains."
>
  <main class="landing-page landing-page--home">
    <section class="hero section">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">Technology. Clarity. Efficiency.</p>
          <h1>Do you feel like you are falling behind on technology?</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            We show you how to use AI and digital tools in a practical way — with less friction,
            clearer processes, and measurable efficiency gains.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Intro%20call">Start a free intro call</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#approach">How we work</a>
          </div>

          <ul class="hero-points" aria-label="Benefits">
            <li>Practical instead of theoretical</li>
            <li>Privacy-aware by design</li>
            <li>Clear next steps instead of tool chaos</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="card-glow"></div>
          <div class="hero-panel">
            <p class="panel-label">Who this is for</p>
            <h2>For companies and individuals who do not need “more tools,” but more orientation.</h2>
            <p>
              If AI, automation, or digital processes are creating more pressure than value right now,
              that is exactly where we start: with clarity, prioritization, and practical solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-alt" id="problem">
      <div class="container narrow">
        <p class="section-kicker">Problem</p>
        <h2>Does any of this sound familiar?</h2>

        <div class="problem-grid">
          <article class="problem-card">
            <p>“Everyone is talking about AI, but I do not know where to start.”</p>
          </article>
          <article class="problem-card">
            <p>“There are plenty of tools, but no clear strategy.”</p>
          </article>
          <article class="problem-card">
            <p>“I am losing time instead of gaining efficiency.”</p>
          </article>
          <article class="problem-card">
            <p>“I am worried about missing something important.”</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <p class="section-bridge">That is exactly where we come in.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="solution">
      <div class="container narrow">
        <p class="section-kicker">Solution</p>
        <h2>A clear path instead of technology chaos</h2>
        <p class="body-large">
          We translate technology trends into concrete, practical steps for your business and daily work.
          No buzzwords. No unnecessary complexity. Just solutions that can actually create momentum.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-alt" id="approach">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-kicker">Approach</p>
        <h2>How we work with you</h2>

        <div class="steps-grid">
          <article class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">01</div>
            <h3>Create clarity</h3>
            <p>
              We analyze your current situation and identify initial quick wins.
              You immediately see where time and effort can be reduced.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">02</div>
            <h3>Build the roadmap</h3>
            <p>
              Concrete tools, processes, and priorities.
              No overload — just structured implementation.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">03</div>
            <h3>Support execution</h3>
            <p>
              Ongoing refinement and adjustment.
              So you do not just catch up technologically — you keep moving forward in a stable way.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="why-us">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-kicker">Why us</p>
        <h2>Why work with us?</h2>

        <div class="trust-grid">
          <article class="trust-card">
            <h3>Practical instead of theoretical</h3>
            <p>
              No abstract trend decks — only concrete applications that actually help in day-to-day work.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-card">
            <h3>Built for your reality</h3>
            <p>
              Solutions must not only work technically. They also need to fit your processes, your team,
              and the way your business actually runs.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-card">
            <h3>Privacy-aware by design</h3>
            <p>
              Especially with AI and digital tools, we take a clean, responsible approach to data in the
              Swiss and EU context.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-card">
            <h3>No blind tool pushing</h3>
            <p>
              We do not recommend trends for their own sake — only what is useful for your specific outcome.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-alt" id="cases">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-kicker">Trust</p>
        <h2>Typical situations where we help</h2>

        <div class="cases-grid">
          <article class="case-card">
            <span class="case-tag">SMBs</span>
            <h3>Too many manual steps in day-to-day operations</h3>
            <p>
              We identify processes that can be meaningfully improved with simple digital tools or AI.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="case-card">
            <span class="case-tag">Teams</span>
            <h3>Uncertainty around AI use and tool selection</h3>
            <p>
              We create orientation, prioritize options, and define a realistic first path forward.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="case-card">
            <span class="case-tag">Leadership</span>
            <h3>Pressure not to fall behind technologically</h3>
            <p>
              We translate trends into concrete decisions instead of burdening your team with more complexity.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section cta-section" id="cta">
      <div class="container cta-box">
        <div>
          <p class="section-kicker">Next step</p>
          <h2>Start with one clear first step</h2>
          <p class="body-large">
            In an intro call, we identify concrete leverage points for more efficiency — with no obligation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Intro%20call">Book an intro call</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/services/">View services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .landing-page--home .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .landing-page--home .steps-grid,
    .landing-page--home .trust-grid,
    .landing-page--home .cases-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>